trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> contains information about the state of a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> che contiene informazioni sullo stato di una classe <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue>.

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to get a collection of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects that represents the state of the workflow queues associated with a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: È possibile chiamare <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> per ottenere una raccolta di oggetti <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> che rappresenta lo stato delle code del flusso di lavoro associate a un'istanza del flusso di lavoro.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the unconsumed items in the workflow queue.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene una raccolta degli elementi non utilizzati nella coda del flusso di lavoro.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> that contains the unconsumed items in the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> contenente gli elementi non utilizzati in <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" /> associated with this <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene il nome dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" /> associato a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection that contains the qualified name each activity subscribed to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene una raccolta che contiene il nome completo di ogni attività sottoscritta a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> that contains the qualified name of the each activity subscribed to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> che contiene il nome completo di ogni attività sottoscritta a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue" />.
